'''Taltmsn Isaggn''' iga yan uḍwar [[Sus|asusi]] itabɛan i taqbilt n [[Isaggn (Ayt Ṣwab)|Isaggn]] [[Ayt Ṣwab]]. Illa uḍwar ad ɣ ammas n idrarn n [[Aṭlas mẓẓiyn|waṭlas mẓẓin]] ɣ udrar n [[Adrar n Lkst|Lkst]] ɣ tmnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Actukn-Ayt Baha|Actukn-Ayt Baha]] ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]].

Ar ittini usiḍn lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2004 mas uḍwar ad zdɣn gis tqriban kran 55 umzdaɣ d 14 n tawjiwin<ref>'''( fr + ar )''' [https://www.webcitation.org/678NyvGs8?url=http://www.lavieeco.com/documents_officiels/Recensement%20population.pdf Asiḍn n n imzdaɣn n Lmɣrib ɣ usggas n 2004] <small>( PDF ) -</small> Tasmirit tamattayt n usɣiws.</ref>.

== Tarakalt ==

Tlla taltmsn ɣ tgrawt n [[Awgnz]], ɣ tmnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Actukn-Ayt Baha|Ctuka-Ayt Baha]], tasga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]], ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]], taggug s 120 km f tmdint n [[Ugadir|Agadir]] ɣ iffus d s 50 km ɣ izzlmḍ n tmdint n [[Tafrawt|Tfrawt]].

