Tugt n imzdaɣ n Taltmsn ar tmuddun s timdinin mqqurnin n tmazirt n Lmɣrib. Llan ɣ [[Ugadir]], [[Mrrakc]], [[Tigmmi tumlilt]], [[Rrbaṭ]], [[Lqnḍṛt]]..., llan akkʷ ma gisn izugn s brra slawann akkʷ [[Fransa]] d [[Marikan]].

