== Tifugliwin ==

Bla ad nbdr tfugliwin tinamurin d tin ddin, da ttḥtafaln Ayt Taltmsn s kigan n tfugliwin yaḍnin zun d ukan :

=== Idrnan ===
Yan wanaw n uɣrum gis tammnt d [[amlu]]. Idrnan ad ar sis ttḥtafaln snat twal ɣ usggʷas, ass n lxmis amzwaru n fibrayr d win mars. Tafugla ad ar gis ittili kraḍ wussan ; ku yan d limkanyat nns d aylli mi iẓḍaṛ ar isbrrak d ar thalla ɣ tazzanin d inbgiwn d iqqbiln.

=== Assifd ===
Fad ad nnurzn yan usggʷas anflaḥ iɣudan, iɛrrimn n udwar ar tmttaln kra n tmɣra nna ɣ ar skarn ɣ kra n ddumya tislit nna d ttasin ɣ kra n lɛmmarya ḥaqqan d ar ttirirn d hḍrn ar d lkmn s uḍar n yan udrar nna ɣ t gis srasn ɣ yan ifri d kra n tɣawsiwin zun d tknarit iqqurn, d lluz, d alim. Ilmma ar taḍun s lmuḍɛ n udwar nna ɣ tkmmaln lhḍrt nnsn 

=== Isswabn ===
Yan wanaw n tfugla nna ɣ lssan middn ihdumn igan fckl; ar sduqqurn f tgmma d ar ttxtaraɛn kra n lqisas issḍṣan fad ad skcmn tumrt ɣ middn n udwar.

=== Lmɛarif ===
Tirmt tamgrut s umata ar tgga [[sksu]] d kra n tfiyya ɣ usklu n yan ''Uxrrub'' imqqurn nɣ d tama n tmzgid nɣ d akkʷ dar usmḍl n ugrram ''Sidi Mussu Brahim'' lli illan ɣ wafa n yan izig ar as ttinin ''Cciɣ''.
* Lmɛruf ''n tiyigiwin'' tamatart n tigira n twuri,
* Lmâarouf ''n ddu tkida'' fad ad ttḥtafaln s ixf usggʷas anflaḥ,
* Lmâarouf ''n Sidi Mussu Brahim'', Ar sis ttḥtafaln imzdaɣ n udwar ad, d Ayt [[Tagḍict (Isaggn)|Tagḍict]], d Ayt [[Ibnnawn (Isaggn)|Ibnnawn]], d Ayt Imi n Tɣzut ɣ imalas wis kraḍ n wayyur n ɣuct.

